Disk World creator help
do_ask

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
do_ask -  Does all the necessary checks to see if he can decorate the requested  surface with the requested decor, handles payment and starts the work.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
int do_ask(string surface,
string decor)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^surface%^RESET%^ - the surface to be decorated 
%^BOLD%^decor%^RESET%^ - the short name of the decor to be used, eg. green carpet

.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/std/npc/surface_decorator.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

Does all the necessary checks to see if he can decorate the requested 
surface with the requested decor, handles payment and starts the work. 

.EP

.SH See also
.SP 5 5
finish_work

.EP

